'<span>ont</span> <span>le</span> <span>même</span> <span>préfixe</span>||<span>qui</span> <span>signifie</span> ''plusieurs'', <span>en</span> <span>latin</span>.||<span>Et</span> <span>ces</span> <span>deux</span> <span>mots</span>-<span>l</span>à<span>utilisent</span> <span>le</span> <span>préfixe</span> ''<span>poly</span>-''||<span>qui</span> <span>signifie</span> <span>également</span> ''plusieurs'',||<span>mais</span> <span>en</span> <span>grec</span> <span>ancien</span>.||<span>Bonjour</span>, <span>madame</span>.||<span>Dans</span> <span>ce</span> <span>cas</span>, ''-chrome'' signifie''couleur'' <span>et</span> ''-glotte'', ''langue''.||<span>Dic</span>, <span>tu</span> <span>es</span> <span>le</span> <span>meilleur</span> .||<span>A</span> <span>toi</span> <span>de</span> <span>jouer</span>, <span>maintenant</span>.||<span>Je</span> <span>te</span> <span>donne</span> <span>un</span> <span>préfixe</span> <span>latin</span> ''-para'',<span>qui</span> <span>signifie</span> ''contre''. <span>Quel</span> <span>mot</span>||<span>peux</span>-<span>tu</span> <span>trouver</span> ?||<span>Et</span> <span>maintenant</span>, <span>avec</span> <span>le</span> <span>préfixe</span> grec''<span>hippo</span>-'' <span>qui</span> <span>signifie</span> ''cheval''.||C''<span>est</span> <span>le</span> ''<span>lieuoù</span> <span>les</span> <span>chevaux</span> courent''.||''<span>Animal</span> <span>dont</span> <span>la</span> <span>têteressemble</span> à <span>celle</span> d''<span>un</span> <span>cheval</span>.''||<span>Merci</span>, <span>Dic</span> .<span>On</span> <span>a</span> <span>vraiment</span> <span>de</span> <span>quoi</span> s''<span>amuser</span>.||<span>Et</span> <span>merci</span> <span>aux</span> <span>Grecs</span> <span>et</span> <span>aux</span> <span>Latins</span>, <span>sansqui</span> <span>le</span> <span>français</span> <span>serait</span> <span>moins</span> <span>riche</span>.', '', 0, '2016-08-19 12:43:13', NULL, 'l-etude-de-l-origine-des-mots-youtube', 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-19 10:43:13', '2016-08-19 10:43:13', '10.76,13.88,17.76,19.28,24.16,25.96,32.36,34,38.8,40.2,44.44,48.52,52.56,56.96,60.48,64.96,66.28,70.52,73.16,78,80.76,84.8,87.8,91.56,94.2,98.48,101.64,103.8,105.48,111,113.6,116.36,121.28,138.4,144.36,149,152.96,156.36', '||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||', 'intermediate', 5, 3, 3, 0, 'b_Sx1i0AoVQ', ''),
(536, 'De l&#39;écriture fractionnaire à l&#39;écriture décimale', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/CcQ8lTdIl-4.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/CcQ8lTdIl-4.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/CcQ8lTdIl-4.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:14,800\r\n-Hé, l''apprenti . Regarde .\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:19,680\r\nC''est ma copine Pasclaire,\nla sorcière.\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:24,320\r\nEt lui, c''est un client\ncomme on en voit souvent.\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:28,800\r\nIl a besoin d''une potion\npour faire pousser les cheveux.\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:32,360\r\nVas-y, récite la recette.\nTu t''en souviens,\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:33,480\r\nj''espère .\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:36,200\r\n-Oui . Potion du poil au caillou.\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:38,760\r\nPour 10 unités de potion,\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:43,239\r\nmélangez dans un récipient,\n3 unités de bave de limace,\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:47,680\r\net 2/10e de jus de moustache\nde chat noir. Et le reste, en eau.\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,200\r\n-Oh . Problème...\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:55,520\r\nTu es sûr de ta recette ?\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:59,920\r\n-Je vais vérifier sur le grimoire\ndes potions, on ne sait jamais.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:04,400\r\nAh... sur le grimoire,\nc''est écrit en écriture décimale,\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:07,240\r\npas en écriture fractionnaire.\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,360\r\n-Ah oui .\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:14,520\r\nC''est grâce à Stevie, le héros\nde la confédération de sorcellerie.\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:18,200\r\n-Stevie ?\nVous voulez dire Stevin de Bruges,\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:20,119\r\nle mathématicien ?\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,720\r\n-Oui, Stevin de Bruges .\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:27,360\r\nAu 16e siècle, il a constaté que\nles commerçants avaient bien du mal\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:30,680\r\nà calculer\navec les fractions décimales.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:35,360\r\nAlors, il a inventé\nune nouvelle façon de les écrire.\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:40,320\r\nCa ne changeait rien aux nombres, sauf\nque c''est une écriture plus simple.\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:43,320\r\nC''est juste une convention.\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:48,600\r\nC''est grâce à Stevin de Bruges\nque l''écriture décimale est née\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,880\r\net qu''on l''utilise encore\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,520\r\naujourd''hui.\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:57,680\r\nPour la recette, je crois\nque j''ai oublié un ingrédient.\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:01,120\r\nJe recommence :\n3 unités de bave de limace,\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:06,880\r\npuis 2/10e de jus de moustache\nde chat noir.\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:13,240\r\nLa fraction décimale 2/10e est égale\nau nombre décimal 0,2 qui se lit :\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,880\r\n0 unité et 2 dixièmes.\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:20,600\r\n-La virgule sépare la partie entière\net la partie décimale.\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:24,320\r\n-Et ne pas oublier :\n4 centièmes de larmes de licorne.\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:31,680\r\nLa fraction décimale 4/100e est égale\nau nombre décimal 0,04 qui se lit :\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:35,000\r\n0 unité et 4 centièmes.\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,920\r\nEt c''est comme ça\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,120\r\nque depuis l''écriture décimale,\r\n\r\n40\r\n00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:43,640\r\net grâce aux recettes correctement\ninscrites dans les grimoires,\r\n\r\n41\r\n00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,960\r\nles sorciers ont des clients\r\n\r\n42\r\n00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,280\r\nheureux .\r\n\r\n', '-<span>Hé</span>, l''<span>appr