>.||<span>Pour</span> <span>comprendretoutes</span> <span>ces</span> <span>explications</span>,||<span>Pik</span> <span>fait</span> <span>appel</span>à <span>ses</span> <span>connaissances</span> <span>précédentes</span>.||<span>Il</span> <span>comprend</span> <span>les</span> <span>mots</span> ''pliage'',''papier'', ''plier'', ''feuille'',||<span>mais</span> <span>aussi</span> <span>les</span> <span>phrases</span> <span>de</span> <span>Pak</span>,<span>qui</span> <span>lui</span> <span>explique</span>||qu''<span>il</span> <span>faut</span> <span>plier</span> <span>la</span> <span>feuilleen</span> <span>deux</span>. <span>Il</span> <span>a</span> <span>vu</span> <span>les</span> <span>gestes</span>||<span>et</span> <span>il</span> <span>sait</span> <span>les</span> <span>reproduire</span>.||<span>Toutes</span> <span>ses</span> <span>connaissances</span> <span>théoriqueset</span> <span>pratiques</span> <span>sont</span> <span>déj</span>à <span>stockées</span>||<span>dans</span> <span>son</span> <span>cerveau</span>,<span>pour</span> <span>servir</span> <span>quand</span> <span>il</span> <span>en</span> <span>a</span> <span>besoin</span>.||C''<span>est</span> <span>sa</span> <span>mémoire</span> <span>sémantique</span>,<span>et</span> <span>quand</span> <span>Pik</span> <span>veut</span> <span>apprendre</span>||<span>quelque</span> <span>chose</span> <span>de</span> <span>nouveau</span>,<span>il</span> <span>va</span> <span>chercher</span> <span>ces</span> <span>éléments</span>||<span>bien</span> <span>rangés</span> <span>dans</span> <span>son</span> <span>cerveau</span>||<span>pour</span> <span>les</span> <span>comparer</span> <span>aux</span> <span>nouveaux</span>.||<span>Ainsi</span>, <span>dans</span> <span>sa</span> <span>mémoire</span> <span>de</span> <span>travail</span>,<span>il</span> <span>peut</span> <span>modifier</span>, <span>agrandir</span>||<span>et</span> <span>renforcerses</span> <span>connaissances</span> <span>du</span> <span>pliage</span>.||<span>Il</span> <span>les</span> <span>stocke</span> <span>pour</span> <span>plus</span> <span>tardgrâce</span> à <span>sa</span> <span>mémoire</span> à <span>long</span> <span>terme</span>,||<span>composée</span> <span>de</span> <span>plusieurs</span> <span>mémoiresspécialisées</span>. <span>Plus</span> <span>on</span> s''<span>en</span> <span>sert</span>,||<span>plus</span> <span>elle</span> s''<span>améliore</span>, <span>comme</span> <span>un</span> <span>sportifqui</span> <span>fait</span> <span>régulièrement</span> <span>du</span> <span>sport</span>.||<span>Ainsi</span>, <span>quand</span> <span>Pik</span> <span>fait</span> <span>de</span> <span>nouveauxpliages</span>, <span>il</span> <span>renforce</span> <span>ses</span> <span>connaissances</span>||<span>dans</span> <span>ce</span> <span>domaine</span>.<span>Il</span> <span>a</span> <span>même</span> <span>appris</span> <span>le</span> <span>mot</span> <span>japonais</span>||''origami'', <span>qui</span> <span>désignel</span>''<span>art</span> <span>du</span> <span>pliage</span>.||<span>Maintenant</span> qu''<span>il</span> <span>sait</span> <span>fairebeaucoup</span> <span>de</span> <span>figures</span>,||<span>il</span> <span>peut</span> <span>en</span> <span>offrir</span> à <span>Paken</span> <span>remerciement</span>.', '', 0, '2016-08-19 12:43:15', NULL, 'savoir-apprendre-la-memoire', 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-19 10:43:15', '2016-08-19 10:43:15', '10.12,12.48,14.72,16.72,20.52,24.64,27.72,31.4,35.56,39,41.2,44.76,48.16,51.16,54.52,57.84,61.32,64.2,67.48,71.32,74.76,77.84,80,84.92,88.16,91,93.64,96.44,98.36,102.88,106,109.36,113.36,117.84,122.08,125,130.039,132.92', '||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||', 'intermediate', 5, 3, 3, 0, 'DDPSFFfOIXw', ''),
(539, 'La 1re personne du singulier (je + e, s, x)', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/dScuAEVJuzA.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/dScuAEVJuzA.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/dScuAEVJuzA.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:15,760\r\n-Ici, le capitaine Kourou,\nj''écoute.\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:18,000\r\nIci, le capitaine Kourou.\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,400\r\nJ''écoute .\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:26,439\r\nLa mission est :\ntrouver l''arbre aux étoiles.\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,080\r\nJe répète.\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:32,640\r\n-''J''écoute'', ''je répète'',\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:36,560\r\nje me souviens\nque la terminaison d''un verbe conjugué\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,760\r\ndépend du verbe à l''infinitif,\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:41,400\r\ndu temps,\nde la personne et du nombre.\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:45,280\r\nMais comment conjugue-t-on ''je'',\nla première personne du singulier,\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:46,480\r\nau présent ?\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:50,480\r\n-Tu te souviens du principal, Lili.\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,320\r\nJe crie : ''Bravo'' .\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:56,160\r\n-Regardez, la terminaison\nest ''e'' pour les trois verbes.\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,840\r\n-Bien vu, Lili .\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:00:58,160 --> 00:01:01,840\r\nC''est le cas pour les verbes\ndont l''infinitif est en ''er''.\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:05,200\r\n''Ecouter'', ''répéter'', ''crier''.\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,560\r\n-Ah, Jules a un indice\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:12,720\r\npour trouver l''arbre aux étoiles.\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,960\r\n''Gravir'', ''ralentir''.\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:18,600\r\nOh . Voilà un nouveau groupe\nde verbes en ''ir'' .\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:22,320\r\n-Nous gravissons et nous ralentissons.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:26,480\r\nCes verbes en ''ir''\nappartiennent au deuxième groupe.\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:30,280\r\nA votre avis, quelle est\nleur terminaison au présent\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,400\r\nde l''indicatif avec le pronom ''je'' ?\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:35,240\r\n-Je gravis, je ralentis...\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:38,640\r\nEuh... Je dirais un ''s''.\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,560\r\n-Au présent de l''indicatif\navec le pronom ''je'',\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:52,360\r\nla terminaison est ''s''\npour ces verbes en ''ir''.\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:57,000\r\n-Allons, Jules,\ncontinue à chercher l''arbre.\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:01:57,320 --> 00:02:00,240\r\nMême si je dois bien avouer\nque je ne vois pas vraiment\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:04,360\r\noù cet arbre aurait pu pousser ici.\nEnfin, je dis ça,\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:07,720\r\nmais je ne connais pas cette planète.\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,039\r\n-Bien joué .\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:13,280\r\nPour les verbes ''devoir'',\n''voir'', ''dire'', ''connaître'',\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:17,560\r\ncomme pour beaucoup d''autres verbes,\nla terminaison est souvent ''s''.\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:21,079\r\nMais il y a encore\nune autre possibilité.\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:24,520\r\nRegarde le verbe ''vouloir''.\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:30,000\r\nAu présent, il prend un ''x'' avec ''je''.\n-J''ai tout compris .\r\n\r\n40\r\n00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:33,079\r\nPour les verbes en ''er'',\nla terminaison\r\n\r\n41\r\n00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:36,800\r\nau présent de l''indicatif\navec le pronom ''je'' est ''e''.\r\n\r\n42\r\n00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:40,720\r\nEt pour tous les autres verbes,\nla terminaison est soit en ''s''\r\n\r\n43\r\n00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:43,799\r\npour un grand nombre de verbes,\nsoit en ''x''.