(548, 'Les homonymes', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/kGZss3tkEU8.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/kGZss3tkEU8.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/kGZss3tkEU8.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:13,360\r\n-Tout le monde est prêt ?\nCa va commencer.\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:16,200\r\nFrançoise, on n''attend que toi.\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:19,520\r\n-Je suis impatient de voir ça,\npetite soeur .\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:22,680\r\n-Tu es prête, Françoise ?\nAlors, voilà :\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:27,000\r\nc''est l''histoire d''un petit marin\nqui veut revoir la terre.\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:30,320\r\nUn jour, il se décide à jeter l''ancre.\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:34,120\r\nMais non, Françoise,\npas l''encre du stylo .\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:37,760\r\nL''ancre du bateau.\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:43,680\r\nJe continue.\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:47,200\r\nLe petit marin,\nlassé de voyager sur la mer,\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:50,440\r\nse dirige vers le port le plus proche.\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:53,760\r\nMais non, Françoise, pas un ''porc'' .\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:58,400\r\nLe port où vont les bateaux.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:00:58,720 --> 00:01:01,480\r\n-Petite soeur,\naux oreilles de Françoise,\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:06,520\r\n''encre'' et ''ancre'', et ''porc'' ou\n''port'' se prononcent de la même façon.\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:10,880\r\nCe sont des ''homonymes'', des mots\nqui ont la même prononciation,\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,800\r\nmais pas le même sens.\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,840\r\n-Comment faire\npour ne pas se tromper ?\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:19,440\r\n-En général,\nils ne s''écrivent pas pareil :\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:32,080\r\n-Je crois que tu t''es encore trompée,\nFrançoise .\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,600\r\n-C''est le port\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,880\r\noù vont les bateaux,\nqui a un ''t'' à la fin.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:40,200\r\n-Et le ''porc'' tout rose,\nlui, il a un ''c''.\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:42,039\r\n-C''est ça, Françoise.\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:45,720\r\nMais si tu doutes\nde l''orthographe des ''homonymes'',\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:49,600\r\nréfléchis à des mots\nde la même famille, pour t''aider.\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:53,040\r\nPar exemple,\nle porc vit dans une porcherie.\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,440\r\n-Et on parle\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,720\r\nde ''zone portuaire''.\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,840\r\n-Bravo, Françoise .\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:02,000\r\nA mon tour de raconter une histoire :\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:05,200\r\nle petit ver vert boit dans un verre.\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:10,560\r\nC''est facile. Tu dois réfléchir\nau sens de la phrase, Françoise,\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,760\r\npour bien différencier\nces ''homonymes'' :\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:18,120\r\nle petit ver de terre,\nvert comme l''herbe,\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:21,040\r\nboit dans un verre, de l''eau.\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,560\r\nBravo . Mais tu sais,\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:28,040\r\nil y a des homonymes qui s''écrivent\net se prononcent de la même façon.\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,960\r\nPar exemple :\r\n\r\n40\r\n00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:35,200\r\nJuliette se regarde dans la glace,\nen mangeant de la glace au chocolat.\r\n\r\n41\r\n00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:38,880\r\n-Ils s''écrivent et se prononcent\nde la même façon,\r\n\r\n42\r\n00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:42,000\r\nmais ils n''ont toujours pas\nle même sens.\r\n\r\n43\r\n00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,239\r\n-Car ce sont des homonymes,\r\n\r\n44\r\n00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:48,280\r\ncomme l''avocat, le monsieur,\net l''avocat, le fruit.\r\n\r\n45\r\n00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:53,000\r\nBravo, Françoise . La prochaine fois,\nje te présenterai les synonymes,\r\n\r\n46\r\n00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:57,440\r\nd''autres mots bien utiles,\npour raconter de belles histoires.\r\n\r\n', '-<span>Tout</span> <span>le</span> <span>monde</span> <span>est</span> <span>prêt</span> ?<span>Ca</span> <span>va</span> <span>commencer</span>.||<span>Françoise</span>, <span>on</span> n''<span>attend</span> <span>que</span> <span>toi</span>.||-<span>Je</span> <span>suis</span> <span>impatient</span> <span>de</span> <span>voir</span> <span>ça</span>,<span>petite</span> <span>soeur</span> .||-<span>Tu</span> <span>es</span> <span>prête</span>, <span>Françoise</span> ?<span>Alors</span>, <span>voil</span>à :||c''<span>est</span> l''<span>histoire</span> d''<span>un</span> <span>petit</span> <span>marinqui</span> <span>veut</span> <span>revoir</span> <span>la</span> <span>terre</span>.||<span>Un</span> <span>jour</span>, <span>il</span> <span>se</span> <span>décide</span> à <span>jeter</span> l''<span>ancre</span>.||<span>Mais</span> <span>non</span>, <span>Françoise</span>,<span>pas</span> l''<span>encre</span> <span>du</span> <span>stylo</span> .||L''<span>ancre</span> <span>du</span> <span>bateau</span>.||<span>Je</span> <span>continue</span>.||<span>Le</span> <span>petit</span> <span>marin</span>,<span>lassé</span> <span>de</span> <span>voyager</span> <span>sur</span> <span>la</span> <span>mer</span>,||<span>se</span> <span>dirige</span> <span>vers</span> <span>le</span> <span>port</span> <span>le</span> <span>plus</span> <span>proche</span>.||<span>Mais</span> <span>non</span>, <span>Françoise</span>, <span>pas</span> <span>un</span> ''porc'' .||<span>Le</span> <span>port</span> <span>où</span> <span>vont</span> <span>les</span> <span>bateaux</span>.||-<span>Petite</span> <span>soeur</span>,<span>aux</span> <span>oreilles</span> <span>de</span> <span>Françoise</span>,||''encre'' <span