(571, 'À tire-larigot', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/srdagIoNg78.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/srdagIoNg78.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/srdagIoNg78.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,680\r\n-Que peut-on faire à tire-larigot ?\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,360\r\nBien des choses.\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:17,840\r\nOn peut prendre des jours de congé\nà tire-larigot,\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:21,360\r\naller au cinéma, faire les soldes\nà tire-larigot.\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:25,280\r\nOn trouve davantage l''expression\nà l''oral qu''à l''écrit.\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:29,680\r\nMais elle sent bon son ancienne langue\net on voit qu''elle a vécu.\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,360\r\nDans son écriture, sa prononciation\net sa construction,\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:36,000\r\nelle est profondément française.\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:38,720\r\nElle fonctionne comme un adverbe.\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:42,960\r\n''A tire-larigot'', c''est-à-dire\n''beaucoup'' et même ''énormément''.\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:47,200\r\nIl y a toujours un effet de sens\nquand on emploie cette formule.\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:51,280\r\nSouvent, on est critique,\nmais on peut être aussi admiratif.\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:54,360\r\nOn souligne\nque la mesure a été dépassée.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:58,680\r\nOn peut faire des affaires\nà tire-larigot, mentir à tire-larigot.\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:02,200\r\nOn ne s''est pas réfréné,\non n''a pas mis de limites.\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:05,120\r\nCa veut presque dire\n''le plus possible''.\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:09,120\r\nSouvent, on emploie cette locution\nquand on mange ou quand on boit.\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:12,360\r\nIl semble qu''il faille\ntrouver là son origine.\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:15,360\r\nLe larigot, jadis, était une flûte,\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:20,800\r\nmais vite, la flûte, comme le larigot\ndésigne un verre contenant du vin.\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:24,560\r\n''Boire à tire-larigot'',\nc''est boire sans s''arrêter.\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:28,839\r\nUn verre après l''autre\nsans détacher la flûte de ses lèvres.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:33,240\r\nEt le verbe ''tirer'' s''accorde bien\nau larigot et à ce genre de sens.\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:36,920\r\nC''est le terme qu''on emploie\npour dire que le liquide\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:39,520\r\npasse d''un contenant dans un autre.\r\n\r\n', '-<span>Que</span> <span>peut</span>-<span>on</span> <span>faire</span> à <span>tire</span>-<span>larigot</span> ?||<span>Bien</span> <span>des</span> <span>choses</span>.||<span>On</span> <span>peut</span> <span>prendre</span> <span>des</span> <span>jours</span> <span>de</span> <span>congé</span>à <span>tire</span>-<span>larigot</span>,||<span>aller</span> <span>au</span> <span>cinéma</span>, <span>faire</span> <span>les</span> <span>soldes</span>à <span>tire</span>-<span>larigot</span>.||<span>On</span> <span>trouve</span> <span>davantage</span> l''<span>expression</span>à l''<span>oral</span> qu''à l''<span>écrit</span>.||<span>Mais</span> <span>elle</span> <span>sent</span> <span>bon</span> <span>son</span> <span>ancienne</span> <span>langueet</span> <span>on</span> <span>voit</span> qu''<span>elle</span> <span>a</span> <span>vécu</span>.||<span>Dans</span> <span>son</span> <span>écriture</span>, <span>sa</span> <span>prononciationet</span> <span>sa</span> <span>construction</span>,||<span>elle</span> <span>est</span> <span>profondément</span> <span>française</span>.||<span>Elle</span> <span>fonctionne</span> <span>comme</span> <span>un</span> <span>adverbe</span>.||''<span>A</span> <span>tire</span>-larigot'', c''<span>est</span>-à-dire''beaucoup'' <span>et</span> <span>même</span> ''<span>énormément</span>''.||<span>Il</span> <span>y</span> <span>a</span> <span>toujours</span> <span>un</span> <span>effet</span> <span>de</span> <span>sensquand</span> <span>on</span> <span>emploie</span> <span>cette</span> <span>formule</span>.||<span>Souvent</span>, <span>on</span> <span>est</span> <span>critique</span>,<span>mais</span> <span>on</span> <span>peut</span> <span>être</span> <span>aussi</span> <span>admiratif</span>.||<span>On</span> <span>souligneque</span> <span>la</span> <span>mesure</span> <span>a</span> <span>été</span> <span>dépassée</span>.||<span>On</span> <span>peut</span> <span>faire</span> <span>des</span> <span>affaires</span>à <span>tire</span>-<span>larigot</span>, <span>mentir</span> à <span>tire</span>-<span>larigot</span>.||<span>On</span> <span>ne</span> s''<span>est</span> <span>pas</span> <span>réfréné</span>,<span>on</span> n''<span>a</span> <span>pas</span> <span>mis</span> <span>de</span> <span>limites</span>.||<span>Ca</span> <span>veut</span> <span>presque</span> dire''<span>le</span> <span>plus</span> possible''.||<span>Souvent</span>, <span>on</span> <span>emploie</span> <span>cette</span> <span>locutionquand</span> <span>on</span> <span>mange</span> <span>ou</span> <span>quand</span> <span>on</span> <span>boit</span>.||<span>Il</span> <span>semble</span> qu''<span>il</span> <span>failletrouver</span> <span>l</span>à <span>son</span> <span>origine</span>.||<span>Le</span> <span>larigot</span>, <span>jadis</span>, <span>était</span> <span>une</span> <span>flûte</span>,||<span>mais</span> <span>vite</span>, <span>la</span> <span>flûte</span>, <span>comme</span> <span>le</span> <span>larigotdésigne</span> <span>un</span> <span>verre</span> <span>contenant</span> <span>du</span> <span>vin</span>.||''<span>Boire</span> à <span>tire</span>-larigot'',c''<span>est</span> <span>boire</span> <span>sans</span> s''<span>arrêter</span>.||<span>Un</span> <span>verre</span> <span>après</span> l''<span>autresans</span> <span>détacher</span> <span>la</span> <span>flûte</span> <span>de</span> <span>ses</span> <span>lèvres</span>.||<span>Et</span> <span>le</span> <span>verbe</span> ''tirer'' s''<span>accorde</span> <span>bienau</span> <span>larigot</span> <span>et</span> à <span>ce</span> <span>genre</span> <span>de</span> <span>sens</span>.||C''<span>est</span> <span>le</span> <span>terme</span> qu''<span>on</span> <span>emploiepour</span> <span>dire</span> <span>que</span> <span>le</span> <span>liquide</span>||<span>passe</span> d''<span>un</span> <span>contenant</span> <span>dans</span> <span>un</span> <span>autre</span>.', '', 0, '2016-08-19 12:43:36', NULL, 'a-tire-larigot', 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-19 10:43:36', '2016-08-19 10:43:36', '10,13,14.68,18.16,21.68,25.6,30,33.68,36.32,39.04,43.28,47.52,51.6,54.68,59,62.52,65.44,69.44,72.68,75.68,81.12,84.88,89.16,93.56,97.24', '||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||', 'intermediate', 5, 3, 3, 0, 'srdagIoNg78', ''),
(572, 'Réception de l’oral, entendre et comprendre', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/StlOlX-IlSU.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/StlOlX-IlSU.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/StlOlX-IlSU.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:12,520\r\n-Pik et Pak\nse comprennent très bien\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,960\r\nquand ils parlent ensemble.\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:18,880\r\nMais le papa de Pak,\nlui, parle une autre langue.\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:20,440\r\n(Langue inconnue.)\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:22,880\r\n-Pak comprend très bien,\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,720\r\nmais Pik ne comprend plus rien.\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:28,800\r\nPik et Pak se demandent\nce qui se passe\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:31,560\r\ndans leur tête\nquand ils entendent des phrases.\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:34,920\r\nQuand Pak parle à Pik dans sa langue,\nelle utilise des mots\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:38,360\r\npour former des phrases\nqui ont un sens.\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:40,800\r\n(Langue inconnue.)\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:43,640\r\n-Bon, nous, on ne comprend rien,\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:46,680\r\nmais Pik, lui, comme nous,\nentend les sons.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,280\r\nIl se souvient des sons de sa langue.\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:52,720\r\nComme il a aussi\nla mémoire des mots,\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:55,040\r\nil reconnaît ces mots.\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:57,560\r\nAinsi, le mot...\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,240\r\n(Langue inconnue.)\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:02,080\r\n-...veut dire ''ballon''\nen langage Pik.\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:06,400\r\nEt il comprend le mot, parce que Pik\na la mémoire du sens des mots.\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:09,920\r\nLe cerveau de Pik peut alors\nreconstruire le sens\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:11,800\r\nde la phrase de Pak.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:14,080\r\n(Langue inconnue.)\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,080\r\n-Là, elle lui a demandé un ballon.\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:20,440\r\nTout cela,\nPik et Pak le font sans effort.\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:23,440\r\nMais comment\nont-ils appris tous ces mots ?\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:28,160\r\nComme nous. Quand Pik et Pak étaient\nencore dans le ventre de leur maman,\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:31,560\r\nils entendaient déjà\ntout ce qu''elle disait.\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:35,320\r\nPlus tard, bébés,\nmême s''ils ne savent pas parler,\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:38,520\r\nils continuent d''entendre\ntous les sons\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:42,360\r\nqui forment des mots,\ndes phrases, des messages.\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:46,000\r\nIls les enregistrent\ndans leur mémoire,\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:49,680\r\net peu à peu en comprennent le sens.\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,680\r\nEt maintenant,\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:55,200\r\nPik et Pak utilisent\nleurs différentes mémoires\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:59,000\r\npour comprendre ce qu''on leur dit\nsans y penser et sans faire d''effort.\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:02,840\r\nC''est aussi pourquoi\nPik ne comprend pas ce que dit\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,479\r\nle papa de Pak.\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:10,000\r\nAlors que Pak a appris\nd''autres sons et d''autres mots\r\n\r\n40\r\n00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:13,560\r\nque Pik n''a pas entendus,\nelle les a mémorisés à son insu.\r\n\r\n41\r\n00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:16,280\r\nC''est pour ça\nqu''elle comprend son papa.\r\n\r\n42\r\n00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:19,400\r\nPar exemple, le mot...\n(Langue inconnue.)\r\n\r\n43\r\n00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:23,000\r\n-...veut dire ''ballon'' en langage Pak.\nMais que se passe-t-il\r\n\r\n44\r\n00:02:23,320 --> 00: