|<span>Oh</span> . <span>Vous</span> <span>rebondisseztous</span> <span>les</span> <span>deux</span> .||-<span>Jules</span> .||<span>Tu</span> <span>dois</span> <span>arrêter</span> <span>de</span> <span>jouer</span> .||<span>Vous</span> <span>devez</span> <span>explorer</span> <span>cette</span> <span>planète</span>.||C''<span>est</span> <span>ce</span> <span>que</span> <span>tous</span> <span>les</span> <span>astronautesdoivent</span> <span>faire</span>.||-<span>Regardez</span>.||<span>Les</span> <span>bases</span> <span>verbalesne</span> <span>sont</span> <span>plus</span> <span>du</span> <span>tout</span> <span>régulières</span>.||-<span>Eh</span> <span>oui</span>. <span>En</span> <span>général</span>, <span>au</span> <span>présent</span>,<span>les</span> <span>verbes</span> <span>comme</span> ''rebondir''||<span>ont</span> <span>deux</span> <span>bases</span> <span>verbales</span>.<span>Certains</span> <span>verbes</span> <span>plus</span> <span>irréguliers</span>||<span>peuvent</span> <span>avoir</span> <span>une</span>, <span>deux</span>, <span>et</span> <span>mêmetrois</span> <span>bases</span>. <span>Comme</span> ''devoir''.||<span>Ils</span> <span>sont</span> <span>rangésdans</span> <span>le</span> <span>troisième</span> <span>groupe</span>.||<span>Ce</span> n''<span>est</span> <span>pas</span> <span>sérieux</span> .||<span>Moi</span>, à <span>votre</span> <span>âge</span>,<span>je</span> <span>volais</span> <span>en</span> <span>fusée</span>.||<span>Je</span> <span>parcourais</span> l''<span>univers</span> .<span>Et</span> <span>je</span> <span>partais</span> à l''<span>aventure</span> .||<span>Et</span> <span>tout</span> <span>ça</span> à l''<span>imparfait</span>.<span>Nous</span> <span>avons</span> <span>changé</span> <span>de</span> <span>temps</span>.||C''<span>est</span> <span>encore</span> <span>le</span> <span>passé</span>,<span>mais</span> <span>le</span> <span>passé</span> <span>simple</span>. <span>Regarde</span> <span>bien</span>.||<span>La</span> <span>base</span> <span>du</span> <span>verbe</span>, <span>elle</span>,n''<span>a</span> <span>pas</span> <span>changé</span>.||-<span>Oh</span>, <span>Alice</span> <span>prend</span> <span>froid</span>.C''<span>est</span> <span>le</span> <span>verbe</span> ''prendre''.||<span>Comment</span> <span>dit</span>-<span>on</span> <span>au</span> <span>passé</span> <span>simple</span> ?-''<span>Elle</span> <span>prit</span>.''||<span>Au</span> <span>passé</span> <span>simple</span>, <span>certains</span> <span>verbesse</span> <span>transforment</span> <span>tellement</span>||qu''<span>on</span> <span>ne</span> <span>les</span> <span>reconnaît</span> <span>plus</span>.-<span>Donc</span>,||<span>pour</span> <span>les</span> <span>reconnaître</span>,<span>il</span> <span>faut</span> <span>les</span> <span>apprendre</span> <span>par</span> <span>coeur</span>.', '', 0, '2016-08-19 12:43:39', NULL, 'structure-du-verbe-conjugue', 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-19 10:43:39', '2016-08-19 10:43:39', '10.12,12.36,15.24,17.84,21.36,25.52,29.8,33.76,37.68,39.84,43.68,46.88,48.8,53.44,56.88,60.24,64.96,68.52,71.16,73.84,75.52,77.84,80.6,84.04,85.16,88.28,92.08,95.72,99.44,103.44,105.36,108.4,112.76,116.76,120.88,125.36,129.28,132.6,136.32,138.68', '||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||', 'intermediate', 5, 3, 3, 0, 'Un1lmZBh10I', ''),
(577, 'Antiquité', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/wjpuPd1LuL8.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/wjpuPd1LuL8.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/wjpuPd1LuL8.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:12,320\r\n-L''Antiquité est une notion historique\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:14,960\r\ndont les contours ont varié\nselon les époques.\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:19,400\r\nLe sens du mot a changé\npar rapport au temps et à l''espace.\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:21,439\r\nS''agissant des pays considérés,\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:26,240\r\non a une constante : la Grèce et Rome\nrestent au centre de cette idée.\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:30,160\r\nViennent s''y agréger d''autres pays,\nselon les intérêts, les connaissances.\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:35,080\r\nL''Egypte des pharaons, et la plupart\ndes civilisations méditerranéennes\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:36,800\r\nqui ont laissé des traces.\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:38,360\r\nOn arrive au début\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:41,840\r\nde ce qu''on appelle ''l''Histoire''\navec ce qu''on suppose être\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:44,360\r\nl''invention de l''agriculture\nen Mésopotamie\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:44,680 --> 00:00:47,200\r\net celle de l''écriture\nchez les Sumériens.\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:50,560\r\nEt l''Asie, alors ?\nElle échappe à cette notion.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:54,360\r\nSi on pense à la Chine,\nà l''Asie du Sud-Est, au Japon,\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:58,240\r\non ne les range pas dans cette\ncatégorie parce que les Occidentaux\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:01,480\r\nne s''intéressent à l''histoire\nasiatique que tardivement\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:05,960\r\net parce que l''Asie ancienne n''est pas\nsentie comme l''ancêtre de l''Europe,\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,720\r\ntrop lointaine et étrangère.\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:10,200\r\nLes origines\nde l''Antiquité sont floues,\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:15,119\r\nmais on semble être plus d''accord\npour savoir quand elle se termine.\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:19,520\r\nLa période de la décadence de l''Empire\nromain : l''installation des barbares\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:22,120\r\nest considérée\ncomme une Antiquité tardive.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:27,679\r\nA partir de 476 et de la déposition\ndu dernier empereur Romulus Augustule,\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,200\r\non passe à une autre période.\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:32,440\r\nMais le mot a une histoire.\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:36,960\r\nMême si ''les Anciens'' est utilisé\nen ancien français pour désigner\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,720\r\nles auteurs latins ou grecs,\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:42,120\r\nl''idée d''Antiquité pour désigner\nune période historique naît\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,440\r\nau 16e siècle avec la Renaissance.\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:49,080\r\nL''Antiquité apparaît alors comme\nune époque mais aussi une référence,\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:52,600\r\nun regard historique\nqui passe au-dessus du Moyen Age,\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:57,920\r\njugé obscur et barbare, et se pose\nsur une période qui servira de modèle.\r\n\r\n', '-L''<span>Antiquité</span> <span>est</span> <span>une</span> <span>notion</span> <span>historique</span>||<span>dont</span> <span>les</span> <span>contours</span> <span>ont</span> <span>variéselon</span> <span>les</span> <span>époques</span>.||<span>Le</span> <span>sens</span> <span>du</span> <span>mot</span> <span>a</span> <span>changépar</span> <span>rapport</span> <span>au</span> <span>temps</span> <span>et</span> à l''<span>espace</span>.||S''<span>agissant</span> <span>des</span> <span>pays</span> <span>considérés</span>,||<span>on</span> <span>a</span> <span>une</span> <span>constante</span> : <span>la</span> <span>Grèce</span> <span>et</span> <span>Romerestent</span> <span>au</span> <span>centre</span> <span>de</span> <span>cette</span> <span>idée</span>.||<span>Viennent</span> s''<span>y</span> <span>agréger</span> d''<span>autres</span> <span>pays</span>,<span>selon</span> <span>les</span> <span>intérêts</span>, <span>les</span> <span>connaissances</span>.||L''<span>Egypte</span> <span>des</span> <span>pharaons</span>, <span>et</span> <span>la</span> <span>plupartdes</span> <span>civilisations</span> <span>méditerranéennes</span>||<span>qui</span> <span>ont</span> <span>laissé</span> <span>des</span> <span>traces</span>.||<span>On</span> <span>arrive</span> <span>au</span> <span>début</span>||<span>de</span> <span>ce</span> qu''<span>on</span> <span>appelle</span> ''l''Histoire''<span>avec</span> <span>ce</span> qu''<span>on</span> <span>suppose</span> <span>être</span>||l''<span>invention</span> <span>de</span> l''<span>agricultureen</span> <span>Mésopotamie</span>||<span>et</span> <span>celle</span> <span>de</span> l''<span>écriturechez</span> <span>les</span> <span>Sumériens</span>.||<span>Et</span> l''<span>Asie</span>, <span>alors</span> ?<span>Elle</span> <span>échappe</span> à <span>cette</span> <span>notion</span>.||<span>Si</span> <span>on</span> <span>pense</span> à <span>la</span> <span>Chine</span>,à l''<span>Asie</span> <span>du</span> <span>Sud</span>-<span>Est</span>, <span>au</span> <span>Japon</span>,||<span>on</span> <span>ne</span> <span>les</span> <span>range</span> <span>pas</span> <span>dans</span> <span>cettecatégorie</span> <span>parce</span> <span>que</span> <span>les</span> <span>Occidentaux</span>||<span>ne</span> s''<span>intéressent</span> à l''<span>histoireasiatique</span> <span>que</span> <span>tardivement</span>||<span>et</span> <span>parce</span> <span>que</span> l''<span>Asie</span> <span>ancienne</span> n''<span>est</span> <span>passentie</span> <span>comme</span> l''<span>ancêtre</span> <span>de</span> l''<span>Europe</span>,||<span>trop</span> <span>lointaine</span> <span>et</span> <span>étrangère</span>.||<span>Les</span> <span>originesde</span> l''<span>Antiquité</span> <span>sont</span> <span>floues</span>,||<span>mais</span> <span>on</span> <span>semble</span> <span>être</span> <span>plus</span> d''<span>accordpour</span> <span>savoir</span> <span>quand</span> <span>elle</span> <span>se</span> <span>termine</span>.||<span>La</span> <span>période</span> <span>de</span> <span>la</span> <span>décadence</span> <span>de</span> l''<span>Empireromain</span> : l''<span>installation</span> <span>des</span> <span>barbares</span>||<span>est</span> <span>considéréecomme</span> <span>une</span> <span>Antiquité</span> <span>tardive</span>.||<span>A</span> <span>partir</span> <span>de</span> <span>476</span> <span>et</span> <span>de</span> <span>la</span> <span>dépositiondu</span> <span>dernier</span> <span>empereur</span> <span>Romulus</span> <span>Augustule</span>,||<span>on</span> <span>passe</span> à <span>une</span> <span>autre</span> <span>période</span>.||<span>Mais</span> <span>le</span> <span>mot</span> <span>a</span> <span>une</span> <span>histoire</span>.||<span>Même</span> <span>si</span> ''<span>les</span> Anciens'' <span>est</span> <span>utiliséen</span> <span>ancien</span> <span>français</span> <span>pour</span> <span>désigner</span>||<span>les</span> <span>auteurs</span> <span>latins</span> <span>ou</span> <span>grecs</span>,||l''<span>idée</span> d''<span>Antiquité</span> <span>pour</span> <span>désignerune</span> <span>période</span> <span>historique</span> <span>naît</span>||<span>au</span> <span>16e</span> <span>siècle</span> <span>avec</span> <span>la</span> <span>Renaissance</span>.||L''<span>Antiquité</span> <span>apparaît</span> <span>alors</span> <span>commeune</span> <span>époque</span> <span>mais</span> <span>aussi</span> <span>une</span> <span>référence</span>,||<span>un</span> <span>regard</span> <span>historiquequi</span> <span>passe</span> <span>au</span>-<span>dessus</span> <span>du</span> <span>Moyen</span> <span>Age</span>,||<span>jugé</span> <span>obscur</span> <span>et</span> <span>barbare</span>, <span>et</span> <span>se</span> <span>posesur</span> <span>une</span> <span>période</span> <span>qui</span> <span>servira</span> <span>de</span> <span>modèle</span>.', '', 0, '2016-08-19 12:43:40', NULL, 'antiquite', 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-19 10:43:40', '2016-08-19 10:43:40', '10.12,12.64,15.28,19.72,21.76,26.56,30.48,35.4,37.12,38.68,42.16,44.68,47.96,50.88,54.68,58.56,61.8,66.28,68.04,70.52,75.44,79.84,82.44,88,90.52,92.76,97.28,99.04,102.44,105.24,109.4,112.92', '||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||', 'intermediate', 5, 3, 3, 0, 'wjpuPd1LuL8', ''),
(578, 'Ranger les mots par ordre alphabétique', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/wtzBV6U9cgY.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/wtzBV6U9cgY.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/wtzBV6U9cgY.mp4', '﻿1\r\n00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:14,720\r\n-Un dictionnaire . Et si on jouait\nà chercher des noms d''animaux ?\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:17,760\r\n(Le chien aboie.)\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:22,240\r\n-Bonne idée. Vas-y, commence .\nTu récites l''alphabet dans ta tête,\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:27,119\r\nje t''arrête, tu me donnes une lettre\net je dois trouver un nom d''animal.\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:32,480 --> 00:00:34,600\r\n-Stop .\n-La lettre D.\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:38,000\r\n-Alors,\nun animal qui commence par D...\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:39,840\r\nLe dauphin.\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:44,120\r\n-Bravo . A toi maintenant\nde réciter l''alphabet.\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:47,400\r\n-A, B, C\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:50,839\r\nD, E, F,\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:54,040\r\nG, et après, ben...\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,560\r\n(Elle chante.)\n-A, B, C, D, E, F, G,\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:00:57,880 --> 00:01:02,480\r\nH, I, J, K, L, M, N, O, P.\nC''est pourtant facile, l''alphabet.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,640\r\nAprès G, c''est H.\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:07,200\r\nH, comme Hippopotame.\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,960\r\n-Je sais bien que les lettres\nsont rangées dans l''ordre.\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:13,280\r\nC''est trop long\npour aller jusqu''au zèbre.\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:16,880\r\n-C''est normal, le Z\nest la dernière lettre de l''alphabet.\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:20,200\r\nIl y a 26 lettres en tout.\nCa fait beaucoup.\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:24,520\r\nIl n''y en a plus que 25, maintenant.\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:28,640\r\nBon allez, c''est encore moi\nqui récite et toi tu trouves l''animal.\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:32,120\r\nMais je ne le fais qu''avec\nles voyelles, c''est plus facile.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:36,800\r\nA, E, I, O, U, Y.\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:41,680\r\n-C''est de la triche . Il n''y a\nque 6 voyelles. C''est trop facile.\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,480\r\n-Allez, les voyelles d''un côté,\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:48,000\r\net les consonnes\ndans le gros tas avec les copains.\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:52,200\r\n-Et, le C, t''as pas l''impression\nqu''il y a un problème ?\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,760\r\n-Allez, les animaux, rangez-vous .\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:59,440\r\n-Rangez-vous tous dans l''ordre\nalphabétique, on s''y retrouvera mieux.\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,440\r\nEn résumé, dans l''alphabet,\nil y a 26 lettres.\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:07,000\r\n-Il y a 6 voyelles.\n-Et 20 consonnes.\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:10,800\r\n-Et toutes les lettres\nsont bien rangées de A à Z.\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,720\r\n-C''est l''ordre alphabétique.\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:17,000\r\n-Eh, le chien et la cigogne,\narrêtez un peu de vous disputer.\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,239\r\n-Comment on fait\npour les ranger dans l''ordre ?\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:22,880\r\nComment on va les trouver dans\nle dictionnaire ? Chien et cigogne ?\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:26,640\r\nTous les deux commencent par C.\nC''est pour ça qu''ils se disputent.\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,120\r\nOn va trouver\ncomment les mettre d''accord.\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:31,640\r\nOn joue à ça la prochaine fois ?\r\n\r\n', '-<span>Un</span> <span>dictionnaire</span> . <span>Et</span> <span>si</span> <span>on</span> <span>jouait</span>à <span>chercher</span> <span>des</span> <span>noms</span> d''<span>animaux</span> ?||(<span>Le</spa